#. type: Title ==
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:233
#, no-wrap
msgid "Data management tools"
msgstr "Herramientas de gestión de datos"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:238
msgid "In this presentation, you will learn about a variety of tools that you can use to improve the quality of your data."
msgstr "En esta presentación, aprenderá sobre diversas herramientas que puede utilizar para mejorar la calidad de sus datos."

#. type: delimited block +
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:246
#, no-wrap
