msgid "For this exercise, you will practice cleaning data using Excel and other helpful tools."
msgstr "En este ejercicio, practicará la limpieza de datos utilizando Excel y otras herramientas útiles."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:401
#, no-wrap
msgid "*Data cleaning with Excel*\n"
msgstr "*Limpieza de datos con Excel*\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:403
msgid "SBN has given you a checklist of data quality elements to verify:"
msgstr "SBN te ha proporcionado una lista de verificación de elementos de calidad de datos para comprobar:"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:405
msgid "All names are correctly spelled and are butterflies"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:406
msgid "All names are complete"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:407
msgid "All coordinates are inside the country stated and converted to decimal format"
msgstr "Todas las coordenadas están dentro del país indicado y convertidas a formato decimal"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:408
msgid "All dates are in the proper column and in the format YYYY-MM-DD"
msgstr "Todas las fechas están en la columna correspondiente y en el formato AAAA-MM-DD"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:410
msgid "Refer to <<Helpful tools>> in order to complete the exercise. It is suggested to use the https://www.gbif.org/tools/species-lookup[GBIF Species Matching tool^], the http://data.canadensys.net/tools/coordinates[Canadensys Coordinate Converter^] and https://maps.google.com/[Google Maps^]. You are not limited to these tools, you may use any tools you like."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:411
msgid "Continue using the same file from the previous exercise."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:412
msgid "Correct any additional errors found in the dataset and document the changes you perform in the exercise sheet."
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:419
msgid "In this presentation, you will learn about https://openrefine.org/[OpenRefine^]. You can use OpenRefine to standardize and improve the quality of your data."
msgstr "En esta presentación, aprenderá sobre https://openrefine.org/[OpenRefine^]. Puede utilizar OpenRefine para normalizar y mejorar la calidad de sus datos."

#. type: delimited block +
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:427
#, no-wrap
msgid "<div class=\"responsive-slides\">\n"
"  <iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/e/2PACX-1vSVDaNu7f19oZEZKfaUqqYKsHoSBgtegqHtvwW7l4TalCyDtzUeiLhGAKsoDOVuEA/embed?start=false&loop=false\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\n"
"</div>\n"
msgstr "<div class=\"responsive-slides\">\n"
"  <iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/e/2PACX-1vSVDaNu7f19oZEZKfaUqqYKsHoSBgtegqHtvwW7l4TalCyDtzUeiLhGAKsoDOVuEA/embed?start=false&loop=false\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\n"
"</div>\n"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:443
#, no-wrap
msgid "data-mobilization::management-openrefine-Slide1.png"
msgstr "data-mobilization::management-openrefine-Slide1.png"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:446
#, no-wrap
msgid "*Slide 1 - Data management - OpenRefine*\n"
msgstr "*Diapositiva 1 - Gestión de datos - OpenRefine*\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:448
msgid "In this presentation, we are going to introduce OpenRefine as a tool for data cleaning."
msgstr "En esta presentación, vamos a presentar OpenRefine como herramienta para la limpieza de datos."

#. type: Target for macro image
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:449
#, no-wrap
msgid "data-mobilization::management-openrefine-Slide2.png"
msgstr "data-mobilization::management-openrefine-Slide2.png"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:452
#, no-wrap
msgid "*Slide 2 - OpenRefine*\n"
msgstr "*Diapositiva 2 - OpenRefine*\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:454
msgid "Previously known as Google Refine; it is now Open access and open sourced. OpenRefine can be used for data cleaning and standardization. You can find it at openrefine.org."
msgstr "Anteriormente conocido como Google Refine, ahora es de acceso abierto y de código abierto. OpenRefine puede utilizarse para la limpieza y normalización de datos. Puede encontrarlo en openrefine.org."

#. type: Target for macro image
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:455
#, no-wrap
msgid "data-mobilization::management-openrefine-Slide3.png"
msgstr "data-mobilization::management-openrefine-Slide3.png"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:458
#, no-wrap
msgid "*Slide 3 - What is OpenRefine?*\n"
msgstr "*Diapositiva 3: ¿Qué es OpenRefine?*\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:460
msgid "OpenRefine is a powerful tool for working with messy data."
msgstr "OpenRefine es una potente herramienta para trabajar con datos desordenados."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:462
msgid "OpenRefine supports faceted browsing as a mechanism for seeing a big picture of your data, and filtering down to just the subset of rows that you want to change in bulk."
msgstr "OpenRefine admite la navegación por facetas como mecanismo para ver un panorama general de los datos y filtrar sólo el subconjunto de filas que desea modificar en bloque."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:464
msgid "The clustering feature works by trying to group the choices in the text facet, so that choices that \"look similar\" get grouped together."
msgstr "La función de agrupación intenta agrupar las opciones en la faceta de texto, de modo que las opciones que \"parecen similares\" se agrupen."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:466
msgid "Reconciliation is a semi-automated process of matching text names to database IDs or keys."
msgstr "La conciliación es un proceso semiautomatizado de cotejo de nombres de texto con identificadores o claves de bases de datos."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:468
msgid "You can use OpenRefine to perform reconciliation of names in your data against any database that exposes a web service following the Reconciliation Service API specification."
msgstr "Puede utilizar OpenRefine para conciliar los nombres de sus datos con los de cualquier base de datos que ofrezca un servicio web conforme a la especificación Reconciliation Service API."

#. type: Target for macro image
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:469
#, no-wrap
msgid "data-mobilization::management-openrefine-Slide4.png"
msgstr "data-mobilization::management-openrefine-Slide4.png"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:472
#, no-wrap
msgid "*Slide 4 - What OpenRefine is not*\n"
msgstr "*Diapositiva 4 - Lo que OpenRefine no es*\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:474
msgid "OpenRefine, however, is not like other tools you’ve used. OpenRefine CANNOT be used for storing or managing data; it is strictly a cleaning and/or standardizing tool."
msgstr "OpenRefine, sin embargo, no es como otras herramientas que haya utilizado. OpenRefine NO puede utilizarse para almacenar o gestionar datos; es estrictamente una herramienta de limpieza y/o normalización."

#. type: Target for macro image
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:475
#, no-wrap
msgid "data-mobilization::management-openrefine-Slide5.png"
msgstr "data-mobilization::management-openrefine-Slide5.png"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:478
#, no-wrap
msgid "*Slide 5 - Feature comparison*\n"
msgstr "*Diapositiva 5 - Comparación de características*\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:480
msgid "As OpenRefine is a different kind of tool, you should consider when it is appropriate to use it versus other tools."
msgstr "Dado que OpenRefine es un tipo de herramienta diferente, debe considerar cuándo es apropiado utilizarla frente a otras herramientas."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:482
msgid "A database provides infrastructure for storage and indexing of data. Generally, it requires programming skills to edit and is absent of easy visualization."
msgstr "Una base de datos proporciona infraestructura para el almacenamiento y la indexación de datos. Por lo general, requiere conocimientos de programación para su edición y carece de una visualización sencilla."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:484
msgid "Excel is a spreadsheet application. It is useful for documenting data and performing operations. And while you can manage your data and have limited ability to clean and standardize your data, it is usually restricted to editing cell by cell. Data is not always visible and it lacks powerful visualization tools."
msgstr "Excel es una aplicación de hoja de cálculo. Es útil para documentar datos y realizar operaciones. Y aunque puede gestionar los datos y tiene una capacidad limitada para limpiarlos y normalizarlos, suele limitarse a editar celda por celda. Los datos no siempre son visibles y carece de potentes herramientas de visualización."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:486
msgid "OpenRefine in contrast offers multi-cell editing, easy exploration and transformation and interactive visualization. But as mentioned previously, it is not for storing and managing data."
msgstr "OpenRefine, en cambio, ofrece edición multicelda, exploración y transformación sencillas y visualización interactiva. Pero, como ya se ha dicho, no sirve para almacenar y gestionar datos."

#. type: Target for macro image
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:487
#, no-wrap
msgid "data-mobilization::management-openrefine-Slide6.png"
msgstr "data-mobilization::management-openrefine-Slide6.png"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:490
#, no-wrap
msgid "*Slide 6 - OpenRefine features*\n"
msgstr "*Diapositiva 6 - Características de OpenRefine*\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:492
msgid "So now that you understand the differences, here is a list of useful features that you will find within OpenRefine. You will soon have an opportunity to complete a tutorial to try all the features."
msgstr "Ahora que ya conoce las diferencias, aquí tiene una lista de funciones útiles que encontrará en OpenRefine. Pronto tendrá la oportunidad de completar un tutorial para probar todas las funciones."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:494
msgid "OpenRefine is a software that you install on your computer. It requires the JAVA JRE/JDK to run. It works on Windows, Mac and Linux."
msgstr "OpenRefine es un software que se instala en la computadora. Requiere JAVA JRE/JDK para funcionar. Funciona en Windows, Mac y Linux."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:496
msgid "As OpenRefine is free and open source, it is supported by a large community of developers and users. It easy to find tutorials online on how to use the tool."
msgstr "Como OpenRefine es gratuito y de código abierto, cuenta con el apoyo de una gran comunidad de desarrolladores y usuarios. Es fácil encontrar tutoriales en línea sobre cómo utilizar la herramienta."

#. type: Target for macro image
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:497
#, no-wrap
msgid "data-mobilization::management-openrefine-Slide7.png"
msgstr "data-mobilization::management-openrefine-Slide7.png"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:500
#, no-wrap
msgid "*Slide 7 - Conclusion*\n"
msgstr "*Diapositiva 7 - Conclusión*\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:504
msgid "This is part of a series of presentations used in the GBIF Biodiversity Data Mobilization course. The biodiversity data mobilization curriculum was originally developed as part of the Biodiversity Information Development Programme funded by the European Union.    This presentation was originally created by Nestor Beltran with additional contributions by Sharon Grant, David Bloom, GBIF Trainers, Mentors and Students. This presentation has been narrated by Laura Anne Russell."
msgstr ""

